nSystem: • ⚠️ DTLX BE API tests — new failures: DTLX Full API Test v2, DTLX BE Fix & Test, DTLX BE Start & Test — all failed (500 `providerSpecificData` error, pre-existing model/provider issue, not new)\nSystem: • ⚠️ cron:ac986a8d — **STILL STUCK** — Telegram delivery retry cron running since ~10:04 UTC (~50 min), attempting to deliver to the now-ended QLHV group session\nSystem: \nSystem: Pipeline: **DEGRADED** ⚠️\nSystem: • Active sessions: 3 (2× 5p crons + 1× Telegram retry cron stuck)\nSystem: • MCP: stitch ✅ confluence ✅ gitlab ✅\nSystem: • Cron: 5p progress ✅ | Daily @ 5AM+7 ✅\nSystem: • Blockers: ⚠️ Stuck Telegram delivery cron | ⚠️ DTLX subagent failures (model/provider errors, persistent baseline)\nSystem: \nSystem: — Orbis 🌐\nSystem: [2026-04-14 10:58:18 UTC] 🟡 Orbis — 5p Update | 10:56 UTC 14 Apr\nSystem: \nSystem: Changes detected:\nSystem: • QLHV group (-5163901258) — **RECOVERED** — session re-spawned ~10:49 UTC, back running ✅\nSystem: • ⚠️ cron:ac986a8d — still stuck since ~10:04 UTC (~52 min), retrying Telegram delivery\nSystem: \nSystem: Pipeline: **DEGRADED** ⚠️ (persistent baseline, no new failures)\nSystem: • Active sessions: 4\nSystem: • MCP: stitch ✅ confluence ✅ gitlab ✅\nSystem: • Cron: 5p progress ✅ | Daily @ 5AM+7 ✅\nSystem: • Blockers: ⚠️ Stuck Telegram delivery retry cron (~52 min) | ⚠️ DTLX subagent failures (model/provider errors — pre-existing)\nSystem: \nSystem: — Orbis 🌐\nSystem: [2026-04-14 11:01:25 UTC] 🟡 Orbis-DTLX — 5p Update | 10:59 UTC 14 Apr\nSystem: \nSystem: Changes detected:\nSystem: • cron:e7885813 (Agent Status) — now running (~10:43 UTC activity), previously captured as done at 10:56 UTC. May have restarted. No new failures detected.\nSystem: • ⚠️ cron:ac986a8d (Telegram delivery retry) — still stuck ~55 min, retrying. Telegram gateway delivery remains unreliable.\nSystem: \nSystem: Pipeline: **DEGRADED** ⚠️\nSystem: • Active sessions: 4\nSystem: • MCP: stitch ✅ confluence ✅ gitlab ✅\nSystem: • Cron: 5p progress ✅ | Da