at 08:32 UTC and has been running for roughly 3 hours.\n\nNow I need to format this as a clean status report and send it to the Telegram user.","thinkingSignature":"c9b5801e562f70db8a54ebfe13da9a6748da90ec9a7a396f54aee9f4990dde7f"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_plc6b4hubrel_1","name":"sessions_send","arguments":{"sessionKey":"agent:master-orchestrator:telegram:direct:6053576134","message":"🌐 Orbis — Agent Status | 11:36 UTC 14 Apr\n\nActive sessions: 3\n• cron:6f3323ef (5p Progress - DTLX): running — Heartbeat monitor, webchat — ~3h 49m\n• cron:ed2d0b5d (5p Progress Report): running — Heartbeat monitor, webchat — ~3h 22m\n• tg-group:-5163901258 (QLHV group): running — Tuition work, 4 sub-agents spawned — ~13m\n\nPipeline: **HEALTHY** ✅\n• MCP: stitch ✅ confluence ✅ gitlab ✅\n• Cron: 5p progress ✅ | Daily @ 5AM+7 ✅\n• Blockers: None\n\n— Orbis 🌐"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":29600,"output":745,"cacheRead":13849,"cacheWrite":297,"totalTokens":44491,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776166614628,"responseId":"062d59d7f87a23e25de25a813d7e9a66"}}
